    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hyperdrive</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">warp-drive efficiency</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">jump distance</span>.",
